{"root":{"data":{"id":"djkqeuwt7h40","created":1782654872687,"text":"周宣王时期的重臣 仲山甫"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djkqfv94h5c0","created":1782654951796,"text":"樊皮 左傳云樊皮不職降爲陽樊"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djkqfz8vae80","created":1782654960487,"text":"樊须 字子迟 孔子72弟子之一"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djkqon7gpxc0","created":1782655639558,"text":"皋"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djkqova82u80","created":1782655657140,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"structure","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}